<div type="old-chinese-contrasts">
<p>Swearing at a person typically and predominantly comes in five ways:</p>
<p>1. declaring him to be vulgar, like a slave etc.;</p>
<p>2. declaring him to be uncivilised, like a barbarian etc.;</p>
<p>3. declaring him to be inhuman, like a wild beast etc.;</p>
<p>4. declaring him to be immoral so as to deserve early death;</p>
<p>5. declaring him unworthy so as to deserve no progeny.</p>
        </div>
